text: Västernorrland County () is a county in northern Sweden, with the seat located in Härnösand. It was established in 1634. == Municipalities == *Härnösand *Kramfors *Sollefteå *Sundsvall *Timrå *Ånge *Örnsköldsvik == References == ==Other websites== Category:1634 establishments in Sweden Category:Västernorrland County
